import { AppBar, Button, Tooltip, Typography } from "@mui/material"
function navBar() {
  return (
    <>
      <AppBar>
        <Tooltip sx={{padding: '10px'}}>
            <Typography variant="h5">LOGO</Typography>
            <Button variant="contained" sx={{float: 'right'}}>Login</Button>
        </Tooltip>
      </AppBar>
    </>
  )
}

export default navBar
